Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 总是说超啊超的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都快成达兹纳大叔的口头禅了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:02:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来变得超可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然看起来很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对拍马屁还真是没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不害臊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是超认真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥在我们国家可是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说如此哦 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去总是自以为是 到处惹事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七班那时真的很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗 那位大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要复仇的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兹卡德大叔 真让人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主张 惹出不少事来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然在此碰见 就说明你的末日到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我族的不共戴天之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔兹 痛快地一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙都想把我生吞活剥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得相当可爱不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 谁让你猜拳输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾鸵鸟一职就非你莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩意外地般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪里般配了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 痛 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从走失的猫到走失的狗 再到走失的猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于轮到走失的鸵鸟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体型变大倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但尽是这些无聊的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力根本无法提升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓任务 并不是用来提升忍者的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和修行可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你急切的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用鸵鸟做对手 来提升你的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 快点开始吧 你不是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里找家旅馆休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟先生也该累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日落之前就能回村了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边怎么了 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…像是在复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇…有人要报仇雪恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光天化日之下 聚众血拼没问题吗 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇许可书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据某些国家规定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当某人被杀害后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许可其遗族进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果持有该国所发的许可证书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在其他国家也能进行复仇行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是那位兹卡德大叔的远房亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜被那个仇家叫了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了 在背后用大石头暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被残忍地杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了追杀仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大叔被族人推选了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个大坏蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金蚊老大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有人在复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来蛮有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得哪方会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说得好…狼总比兔子跑得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未必哦 仇敌一方似乎胸有成竹 面不改色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可报不了仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混账…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门外汉给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是有过34回复仇经验的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是失败34回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 我都要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要替族人鹿藏大叔报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后偷袭的卑鄙行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果此仇无法昭雪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话对我太过残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试又怎么能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次或许就能成功复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会运用全部的忍者技能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮大叔成为一代复仇宗师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在逞能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就暂时交给鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先回旅馆休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 安心交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔的复仇愤怒指标不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应当无论何时都能瞬间爆发出怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样面对突如其来的复仇 就不会手忙脚乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来背你这混蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋要去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去那旁边的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再远点也没关系啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么觉得有点…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是丁点的仇恨 也不能轻易放过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让复仇融入生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞肩之恨 撞肩之仇 撞肩之怨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中要充满了对敌人的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而将那股怨恨淋漓尽致地发泄于手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 被憎恨的仇家怎么会如此清秀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔果然不适合当复仇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不适合当教官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何如此执着于复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我无脸返回家乡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想尽快了结此事 然后回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到年迈的父母的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏身手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还呆着干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟咬断了绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然身手不凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔明明那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么始终不能复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当看到那家伙的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量就逐渐消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神…那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔在那之后怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计为了复仇 再度启程了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会永远持续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 想报仇的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被你的真诚所打动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你完成复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这家伙带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请毫无顾忌地来场复仇之战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗要让我们金蚊一家来组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗到底谁是最后的赢家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下注吧 下注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪一边比较强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是仇家更厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大叔太无能了 毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我赌仇家500两
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那赌金少的一方就算我金蚊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那大叔使出真本领的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我大赚一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然利用大叔的复仇来赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切到此为此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意 我不会轻易被你杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 不看对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说鸣人的指导奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…总觉得这场决斗让人很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正像大叔所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的脸…眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要流露出那样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明可能被我杀掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不打算伤害大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都无法对他下手的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔现在应该心知肚明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 刀刃是钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是不会杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个双胞胎弟弟 名叫影木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影木曾借钱给你族的鹿藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因生了孩子急需用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便前去催促还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而鹿藏却装傻 矢口否认借钱一事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果两人起了争执 一起倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而鹿藏倒地时 碰到了晒干货的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说这是意外事故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影木打算去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从证据来看 他毫无疑问是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定代替他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而弟弟则同他的妻子以及刚出生的孩子隐姓埋名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则故意暴露身份 吸引追杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让那样的好人糟蹋了人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个恶人 给社会 家人 朋友添尽了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来赎罪 再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都是我弟弟的片面之词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有真凭实据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信由你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信的话 就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就姑且信你一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你… 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对复仇有些厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 你都装作有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就由我来装作复仇好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 你都要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然 你们可就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…来拔刀相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我想要早些回村子里修行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来参合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吧 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他俩决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不得不报之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我还太幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是卡卡西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为木叶发生了大事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要马上赶来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟他聊聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事…事实上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助他…这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助呢 因为跟我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 很快就会把他给带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他回来后再跟他打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时佐助也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 因为三角关系闹出纠纷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌 才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有父母兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有羁绊才会感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦失去羁绊又将如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在能够了解了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓复仇到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解一些痛楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有承受过相同的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法真正的理解他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以为自己很了解佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可实际上我根本不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 无论我在终结之谷对佐助说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都无动于衷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了解佐助的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能跟他一同欢笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连跟他打架的资格都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之后我想跟他好好地打一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会让佐助回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七班的所有人也能一起欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇合地点的确就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我们先到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的协作任务竟然迟到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐真的有意向木叶修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到和这家伙合作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗 羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟国的伙伴们 大家要好好相处啊
